I"p<p>It only takes about 10 min to make a stove that burns methylated spirits from a coke can.</p>

<!-- more -->

<p>There are several variations but I wanted to use a standard 375 ml can and 
for it to be as simple as possible. The stove below is based on a
video linked at the end of this post.</p>

<p>First score the top of the can as shown, keep doing it until you can break
through and neatly cut off the top of the can.</p>

<figure class="">
  <a href="/assets/images/2020/05/stove1.jpeg">
